{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/civil-nuclear-constabulary/about/procurement","content_id":"5f65b4c4-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef","description":"Supplying goods and services to the Civil Nuclear Constabulary (CNC).\r\n","details":{"attachments":[{"accessible":false,"alternative_format_contact_email":"press.office@cnc.pnn.police.uk","assets":[{"asset_manager_id":"618298398fa8f5297a62a340","filename":"Shortform_Terms_and_Conditions_Goods_FINAL.pdf"},{"asset_manager_id":"618298398fa8f52978e14cc1","filename":"thumbnail_Shortform_Terms_and_Conditions_Goods_FINAL.pdf.png"}],"attachment_type":"file","content_type":"application/pdf","file_size":205812,"filename":"Shortform_Terms_and_Conditions_Goods_FINAL.pdf","id":"6391998","number_of_pages":14,"title":"Short form terms and conditions - goods","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/618298398fa8f5297a62a340/Shortform_Terms_and_Conditions_Goods_FINAL.pdf"},{"accessible":false,"alternative_format_contact_email":"press.office@cnc.pnn.police.uk","assets":[{"asset_manager_id":"6182984dd3bf7f56020e5061","filename":"Shortform_Terms_and_Conditions_Services_FINAL.pdf"},{"asset_manager_id":"6182984d8fa8f52986e61e6e","filename":"thumbnail_Shortform_Terms_and_Conditions_Services_FINAL.pdf.png"}],"attachment_type":"file","content_type":"application/pdf","file_size":218037,"filename":"Shortform_Terms_and_Conditions_Services_FINAL.pdf","id":"6391999","number_of_pages":18,"title":"Short form terms and conditions - services","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6182984dd3bf7f56020e5061/Shortform_Terms_and_Conditions_Services_FINAL.pdf"}],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><h2 id=\"doing-business-with-the-cnc\">Doing business with the <abbr title=\"Civil Nuclear Constabulary\">CNC</abbr>\n</h2>\n\n<p>Our contracts and procurement team prepares tenders, drafts terms and evaluates offers.</p>\n\n<p>We may post tender notices through:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.blpd.gov.uk/logon.aspx?ReturnUrl=%2fdefault.aspx\" class=\"govuk-link\">the Bluelight ProContract website</a></li>\n  <li>\n<a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.ojec.com/\" class=\"govuk-link\">the Official Journal of the European Union</a>, where required by the European Union Procurement Directive</li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/contracts-finder\" class=\"govuk-link\">Contracts Finder</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>There are a number of opportunities coming up as follows</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Radio Equipment for the Site Security Control Rooms</li>\n  <li>Employee Assistance Programme</li>\n  <li>MOE Shotguns</li>\n  <li>Survey Software</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>If you’re interested in either of these procurement opportunities send an email to <a href=\"mailto:procurement@cnc.pnn.police.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\">procurement@cnc.pnn.police.uk</a> with the specific procurement opportunity referenced in the subject line.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"standard-supplier-terms-and-conditions\">Standard supplier terms and conditions</h2>\n\n<p>Purchases we make are subject to our terms and conditions, but some purchases may be subject to a special set of terms and conditions.</p>\n\n<section data-module=\"ga4-link-tracker\" class=\"gem-c-attachment govuk-!-margin-bottom-6\">\n  <div class=\"gem-c-attachment__thumbnail govuk-!-display-none-print\">\n    <a class=\"govuk-link\" target=\"_self\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-ga4-link='{\"event_name\":\"file_download\",\"type\":\"attachment\"}' href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/618298398fa8f5297a62a340/Shortform_Terms_and_Conditions_Goods_FINAL.pdf\">\n        <svg class=\"gem-c-attachment__thumbnail-image gem-c-attachment__thumbnail-image--pdf\" version=\"1.1\" viewbox=\"0 0 99 140\">\n  <path d=\"M12,59h9v9h-9v-9ZM30,77v9h39v-9H30ZM30,104h57v-9H30v9ZM30,122h48v-9H30v9ZM12,86h9v-9h-9v9ZM12,122h9v-9h-9v9ZM12,104h9v-9h-9v9ZM30,68h57v-9H30v9ZM35.2,21c-.3-.2-.6-.4-1-.5s-.8-.2-1.3-.2h-2.6v5.5h2.6c.5,0,1,0,1.3